2つの微分可能な連続実数値関数\(f(x,y),g(x,y)\)とし, 以下のような微分可能な連続実数値関数を用意する. \[ {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda) = f(x,y) - \lambda g(x,y) \] 上記の偏微分が\((x,y,\lambda) = (a, b, l)\)のとき, \[ \left. rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial x}ight|_{(a,b,l)} = \left. rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial y}ight| _{(a,b,l)} = \left.  rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial \lambda} ight| _{(a,b,l)} = 0 \] が成立する場合,\((x,y,\lambda) = (a, b, l)\)で\(f(x,y)\)は,\(g(x,y) = 0\)の拘束条件で極値を取る. 証明 連立方程式は, \[ \left\{  egin{array}{ll} \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial \lambda} ight| _{(a,b,l)} &= g(a,b) = 0 \ \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b,l)} &= \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b,l)} - \lambda \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b,l)} = 0 \ \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial {\mathscr L}(x,y,\lambda)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b,l)} &= \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b,l)} - \lambda \left. \displaystyle  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b,l)} = 0 \end{array} ight. \] 拘束条件は,第1式が満たしている.\(( rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x}, rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}) = (0,0)\)ならば,\(g(x,y)\)が定数を表しているので,\(x,y\)を拘束せず, 拘束条件のない極値を求める問題となる. \(\left(\left.  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x}ight|_{(a,b)}, \left. rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}ight| _{(a,b)} ight) 
