ot = 0\)とする. 前述の仮定と陰関数定理より,\(a,b\)の近傍で微分可能な連続関数\(y=h(x)\)が存在する. \(h\)は微分可能で,\(g(x,y) = 0\)なので, \[  rac{d g(x,y)}{d x} =  rac{d g(x,h(x))}{d x} =  rac{\partial g}{\partial x} +  rac{\partial g}{\partial y} rac{d h}{d x} = 0 \] から, \[  rac{d h(x)}{d x} = - rac{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}} \] また,\(f(x,y) = f(x,h(x))\)と書くことができ, \[  rac{d f(x,y)}{d x} =  rac{d f(x,h(x))}{d x} =  rac{\partial f}{\partial x} +  rac{\partial f}{\partial y} rac{d h}{d x} \] これが,\((x,y) = (a,b)\)で極値を取るなら, \[ \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} + \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}  rac{d h(x)}{d x} ight| _{(a,b)} = 0 \] \(\displaystyle  rac{d h(x)}{d x} = - rac{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}}\)から, \[ \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} - \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}  rac{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}} ight| _{(a,b)} = \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} - \left.  rac{ rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}} rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} = 0 \] ここで,\(\displaystyle l=\left.  rac{ rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}}ight| _{(a,b)}\)とおくと, \[ \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} - \left. l  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b)} = \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b,l)} - \lambda \left.  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial x} ight| _{(a,b,l)} = 0 \] 第2式が成立し,第3式は, \[  egin{align} \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b,l)} - \lambda \left.  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b,l)} &= \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b)} - l \left.  rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b)} \ &= \left.  rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y} ight| _{(a,b)} - \left.  rac{ rac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}}{ rac{\partial g(x,y)}{\partial y}}  rac{\partia